Link for the APK:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1stvXAiVtzJgHYjA8zSwcxSf1L_wLtf41/view?usp=sharing

You just need to download and install this apk on your smartphone (Version should be greater than Android Kitkat), and just run the app and allow camera access.
After that in app, click on open Gift and then scan those 4 images (Pic1, Pic2, Pic3, Pic4) with your camera, and you will see the magic ;)
